#

Grilled Chicken Avocado Burger with Jalapeño and Chipotle Mayo

$12.5
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

EggDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

GrilledBurgerSpicyHealthy

Description

A juicy grilled chicken burger topped with creamy avocado, spicy jalapeño, and a smoky chipotle mayo, served on a lettuce wrap.

Ingredients

  • Boneless, skinless chicken breast: 1 lb
  • Avocado: 1 large
  • Jalapeño: 1, finely chopped
  • Chipotle in adobo sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Mayonnaise: 1/4 cup
  • Lettuce leaves: 4 large
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Lime juice: 1 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
